nodes.name: base_model.0
nodes.class_name:
ConvEmbeddingInputLayer(
  (embeddings): ModuleDict(
    (active_player_t-0): Embedding(2, 32)
    (active_player_t-1): Embedding(2, 32)
    (active_player_t-2): Embedding(2, 32)
    (active_player_t-3): Embedding(2, 32)
    (inactive_player_t-0): Embedding(2, 32)
    (inactive_player_t-1): Embedding(2, 32)
    (inactive_player_t-2): Embedding(2, 32)
    (inactive_player_t-3): Embedding(2, 32)
    (p1_active): Embedding(2, 32)
  )
  (continuous_space_embedding): Sequential(
    (0): Conv2d(1, 128, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    (1): LeakyReLU(negative_slope=0.01)
  )
  (embedding_merger): Sequential(
    (0): Conv2d(288, 128, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    (1): LeakyReLU(negative_slope=0.01)
  )
  (merger): Sequential(
    (0): Conv2d(256, 128, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
  )
)

nodes.name: base_model.1
nodes.class_name:
ResidualBlock(
  (conv1): Conv2d(128, 128, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
  (norm1): Identity()
  (act1): LeakyReLU(negative_slope=0.01)
  (conv2): Conv2d(128, 128, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
  (norm2): Identity()
  (final_act): LeakyReLU(negative_slope=0.01)
  (change_n_channels): Identity()
  (squeeze_excitation): SELayer(
    (fc): Sequential(
      (0): Linear(in_features=128, out_features=8, bias=False)
      (1): ReLU(inplace=True)
      (2): Linear(in_features=8, out_features=128, bias=False)
      (3): Sigmoid()
    )
  )
)
